ost.com/entry/rolling-stones-photo-aftermath_n_2885956|accessdate=26 November 2018|first=Michelle|date=15 April 2013|website=[[The Huffington Post]]|title=See The Rolling Stones Before They Released 'Aftermath' (PHOTO)|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181127151901/https://www.huffpost.com/entry/rolling-stones-photo-aftermath_n_2885956|archive-date=27 November 2018|url-status=live}}\n* {{cite news|ref=harv|last=Petridis|first=Alexis|authorlink=Alexis Petridis|date=17 May 2018|url=https://www.theguardian.com/music/2018/may/17/the-rolling-stones-every-album-ranked|title=The Rolling Stones \u2013 every album ranked!|newspaper=[[The Guardian]]|accessdate=2 January 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191017053038/https://www.theguardian.com/music/2018/may/17/the-rolling-stones-every-album-ranked|archive-date=17 October 2019|url-status=live}}\n* {{cite book|last=Philo|first=Simon|title=British Invasion: The Crosscurrents of Musical Influence|url=https://books.google.com/?id=WqiDBQAAQBAJ|year=2015|publisher=Rowman & Littlefield|location=Lanham, MD|isbn=978-0-8108-8627-8|ref=harv|via=Google Books}}\n* {{cite magazine|ref=harv|first=Jody|last=Rosen|title=The Rolling Stones Part 1: The 1960s and '70s|magazine=[[Blender (magazine)|Blender]]|date=2 July 2006|url=http://www.blender.com/guide/back-catalogue/68202/rolling-stones-smallpart-1-1960s-14670ssmall.html|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101227005517/http://www.blender.com/guide/back-catalogue/68202/rolling-stones-smallpart-1-1960s-14670ssmall.html|archivedate=27 December 2010|accessdate=12 January 2020}}\n* {{cite news|ref=harv|last=Ross|first=Graeme|date=12 December 2018|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/music/playlist-10-best-rolling-stones-albums-a8680051.html|title=Playlist: The 10 best Rolling Stones albums|newspaper=[[The Independent]]|accessdate=19 March 2020}}\n* {{cite book|first=Chris|last=Salewicz|authorlink=Chris Salewicz|title=Mick & Keith|publisher=Orion|location