aph.co.uk/music/what-to-listen-to/rolling-stones-defining-moments/aftermath-released-1966although-their-first-two-albums--the-roll/|archive-date=31 August 2018|url-status=live}}\n* {{cite web|ref={{SfnRef|Anon. (a)|n.d.}}|author=Anon.|date=n.d.|url=https://www.bpi.co.uk/brit-certified/|title=British album certifications \u2013 The Rolling Stones \u2013 Aftermath|publisher=[[British Phonographic Industry]]|accessdate=4 February 2020|at=''Select ''albums'' in the Format field. Select ''Silver'' in the Certification field. Type ''Aftermath'' in the \"Search BPI Awards\" field and then press Enter.''}}\n* {{cite web|ref={{SfnRef|Anon. (b)|n.d.}}|author=Anon.|date=n.d.|url=http://www.charts-surfer.de/musiksuche.php|title=Charts-Surfer: Liedsuche|publisher=charts-surfer.de|language=German|accessdate=7 January 2020|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/65p9Vuyxi?url=http://www.charts-surfer.de/musiksuche.php|archive-date=29 February 2012|url-status=live}}\n* {{cite web|ref={{SfnRef|Anon. (c)|n.d.}}|author=Anon.|date=n.d.|title=Key Dates in the History of the Official UK Charts|url=http://www.theofficialcharts.com/company_history.php |publisher=[[Official Charts Company]]|accessdate=15 August 2015 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080110032725/http://www.theofficialcharts.com/company_history.php|archivedate=10 January 2008}}\n* {{cite web|ref={{SfnRef|Anon. (d)|n.d.}}|author=Anon.|date=n.d.|url=https://www.officialcharts.com/artists/|title=UK charts archive|publisher=Official Charts Company|accessdate=23 March 2010|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190508182655/https://www.officialcharts.com/artists/|archive-date=8 May 2019|url-status=live}}\n* {{cite web|ref={{SfnRef|Anon. (e)|n.d.}}|author=Anon.|date=n.d.|url=https://www.riaa.com/gold-platinum/?tab_active=default-award&ar=The+Rolling+Stones&ti=Aftermath#search_section|title=American album certifications \u2013 The Rolling Stones \u2013 Aftermath|publisher=[[Recording Industry Association of America]]|acc